The most often consumed snack is the Osmania Biscuit, which has developed into a distinctive dish with a distinct heritage. Dietitians initially made these cookies as a snack that was somewhat sweet and salty. These spherical cookies go perfectly with chai because of their distinctive sweet and salty flavour combination and round form.
